languages.text: "Надо же, и кому ты могла сдаться?"

traits.locale_text: "Надо же, и кому ты могла сдаться?"

languages.text: "Addressed to you? What nonsense! Who would send you a message?"
languages.original_text: "Надо же, и кому ты могла сдаться?"

traits.locale_text: "You don't say. Who could have wanted you?"
"You don't say. Who could have wanted you?"
"Is that so? And whom exactly would you have surrendered to?"
"Is that so? And whom exactly would you have surrendered to?"

languages.text: “有人找你？简直是胡说八道！到底是什么人想找你？”
languages.original_text: "Addressed to you? What nonsense! Who would send you a message?"

traits.locale_text: “有人找你？简直是胡说八道！到底是什么人想找你？”

languages.text: « Vraiment ? Et qui pourrait bien avoir besoin de vous ? »
languages.original_text: "Is that so? And whom exactly would you have surrendered to?"

traits.locale_text: « Vraiment ? Et qui pourrait bien avoir besoin de vous ? »

languages.text: «¿Dirigido a usted? ¡Ridículo! ¿Quién le enviaría un mensaje?».
languages.original_text: "Addressed to you? What nonsense! Who would send you a message?"

traits.locale_text: «¿Dirigido a usted? ¡Ridículo! ¿Quién le enviaría un mensaje?».

languages.text: 「あなたに向けて？そんな馬鹿な！あなたにメッセージを送る人なんていると思いますか？」
languages.original_text: "Addressed to you? What nonsense! Who would send you a message?"

traits.locale_text: 「あなたに向けて？そんな馬鹿な！あなたにメッセージを送る人なんていると思いますか？」

languages.text: "Ach, wirklich? "Und wem genau hättet Ihr Euch ergeben?"
